org.opendaylight.controller.md.sal.binding.api

接口 ClusteredDataTreeChangeListener<T extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject>

  • 类型参数:
    T - the DataObject type
    所有超级接口:
    DataTreeChangeListener<T>, EventListener
    已过时。 
    Use ClusteredDataTreeChangeListener instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface ClusteredDataTreeChangeListener<T extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.DataObject>
extends DataTreeChangeListener<T>
    ClusteredDataTreeChangeListener is a marker interface to enable data tree change notifications on all instances in a cluster where this listener is registered.

    Applications should implement ClusteredDataTreeChangeListener instead of DataTreeChangeListener, if they want to listen for data tree change notifications on any node of a clustered data store. DataTreeChangeListener enables notifications only at the leader of the data store.

    作者:
    Thomas Pantelis
